{
  "stem": "232.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were guarded by-- you can see the guard post here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were standing with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Each-- each guard had a-- a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the guard would-- two guards with dogs were walking between the electric wires.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wherever there was a double line, they were walking with the dogs to check.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was not a picnic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were laying-- we were laying in bunks, in wooden bunks, nine in a row, when-- three high.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you were laying first row, you-- you go in the bunk, you-- you lay down with people you don't know, and you come from the outside world, maybe the other ones came from other camps or from-- from ghettos.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came really from-- from-- from a country we were not in a camp there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very weird to be-- be laying down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could not move.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can only turn around when the end decide to turn, everybody had to turn over too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't lay in the width because there wasn't enough room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they gave you for nine people, three or four blankets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you were in the middle, you always knew that you'd get a piece of blanket, that you will be warm.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when you were on the two outsides, you know you will be at night without a blanket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then you are laying with your knees to your belly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you're shivering because they didn't heat the-- the barracks there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So, of course, the new-- the new ones, who they called the [NON-ENGLISH], we were always on the end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And sometimes-- sometimes from the weight of the people, if the one board breaks, all nine fell on the nine below.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the nine below fall.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
